quran[24]{c,v,t}:
  18,75,"[Khadiru] wi'i: \"Enee, mi wi'aano ma pellet, an a hattantaake mu√±al wonndugol e an"
  18,76,"[Muusaa] maaki: \"Si mi lanndike ma gaayi huunde …ìaawo …óii, haray wata a wonndino e an, gom…óii a timminii nganto e an"
  18,77,"∆Åe yahi haa …ìe yaltiti e yim…ìe saare, …ìe …óa…ì…ìiri …ìe √±aametee …ìe salii wernude …ìe, …ìe tawi e nder mayre maadi faalaa fukkaade [Khadiru] o darnindi , o [Muusaa] maaki: \"Sinno a yi…óuno a ∆¥ettayno njoddi e …óun"
  18,78,"[Khadiru] maaki: \"Ko …óum woni seedigal hakku- nde an e ma'a, aray mi yiito maa firo kon ko a hattananooka mun√±aade e dow mun"
  18,79,"Si ko laana kan, ka laatanike miskinee…ìe gollo- …ìe ka maayo, mi faalaa aybinnde ka, hari laatike …ìaawo ma…ì…ìe lam…óo himo nannga kala laana o ja…ìta"
  18,80,"Si ko suka on maw…ìe makko …ìen wonii gom…óim…ìe , men huli wata o fawu …ìe bewre e keeferaaku"
  18,81,Men faalaa nde Joomi ma…ì…ìe wa…ótitanta …ìe …ìur…óo mo mo∆¥∆¥ude laa…ìu…óo e …ìur…óo …ìattaade yurmeende
  18,82,"Si ko maadi ndin, ndi laatanino sukaa…ìe …ói…óo won…óu…ìe ka saare, laatii ley mayri ngalu ma…ì…ìe kam…ìe …ói…óo, hari baaba ma…ì…ìe laatinoke mo∆¥∆¥o, Joomi maa…óa Faalaa nde …ìe yottotoo sagatalaaku ma…ì…ìe, O yaltina ngalu ma…ì…ìe ngun […óum] ko Yurmeende immorde ka Joomi maa, mi wa…óiraali …óum e yamirooree an, …óum ko firo kon ko a hattanaali mun√±aade e dow mun"
  18,83,"Hi…ìe fa'umaa lanndaade fii Julqarnayni, maaku: \"Aray mi jannga e taweede mon e …óun janta"
  18,84,"Menen, Men wee…ìinanno mo ka leydi, Men Okki mo immorde e kala huunde sabu"
  18,85,O jokki sabu
  18,86,"Haa nde o yottinoo ka mutirde naange ngen o tawi hinge muta e loope …ìaleeje, o tawi ton yim…ìe : Men wi'i: \"Ko an yo jom galaa…ói …ói…ói, ko si a leptay maa…óun si a jogitoto e ma…ì…ìe ko mo∆¥∆¥i"
  18,87,"O wi'i: Si tawii ko on too√±u…óo aray men lepta mo, refti o ruttee ka Joomi makko O lepta mo lepte a√±ii…óe"
  18,88,"Si tawii ko on gom…óin…óo o golli ko mo∆¥∆¥i no woodani mo njo…ìdi mo∆¥∆¥iri ndin, aray Men wi'ana mo e fiyaake Amen on neweende"
  18,89,Refti o jokki laawol
  18,90,"Haa nde o yottinoo ka ∆¥ellitorde naange ngen, o tawi hinge ∆¥ellitoo e dow yim…ìe, Men wa…óanaali …ìe gaanin magge heedo"
  18,91,"Ko wano nii, gom…óii Men hu…ìindike ko woni kon ka makko e ganndal. @Corrected"
  18,92,Refti o jokki laawol
  18,93,Haa nde o yottinoo hakkunde heedooji …óin …ói…óio tawi gaanin majji yim…ìe …ìe …óe…ìataa faamude konngol
  18,94,"∆Åe wi'i: \"Ko an Julqarnayni, pellet, Yaajuuja e Maajuuja ko bonnoo…ìe ka leydi. Enee, men wa…óante ngeenaari fii yo a wa…óu hakkunde amen e ma…ì…ìe heedo"
  18,95,"O wi'i: \"Ko Joomi am wee…ìinani lan kon …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude, walliree lan doole mi wa…óa hakkunde mo'on e ma…ì…ìe heedo"
  18,96,"Addanee lam kunte njam…óe haa nde o feppi- ndirnoo hakkunde na…óe …óen …ói…ói, o wi'i: \"Wifee haa nde o wa…óunoo …óum yiite, o wi'i: addanee lam sila mi wancina e dow mun"
  18,97,"∆Åe hattantaake ∆¥ellitagol ndi, …ìe hattantaake kadi yulugol ndi"
  18,98,"O wi'i: …óum …óoo ko Yurmeende immornde e Joomi am, si Fodoore Joomi am nden arii O wa…óay [heedo] ngon …óiggungo, Fodoore Joomi am nden laatike ko nde Goonga"